org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl
Class AeAbstractLockManager.AeLock

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.AeAbstractLockManager.AeLock
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeLockManager.IAeLock
Enclosing class:
AeAbstractLockManager
public static class AeAbstractLockManager.AeLock
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAeLockManager.IAeLock

This class implements a simple lock object which contains both a QName and correlation hash. It also has a reference counter which is used to keep track of the number of references to the lock. When the reference count reaches zero then the lock can be released.
